Make windows mutexes use CRITICAL_SECTION objects.

Also added TryLock method to NaClFastMutex objects.  If we later
change NaClFastMutex objects to be spinlocks, then we will need to
move the CRITICAL_SECTION code inside the lock_impl_win.cc file.

